sentence: denny j sandoval| denny j sandoval, 56, of hero street in silvis, il, died saturday, june 6, 2015, at his home.
he is the son of rita and joseph sandoval of silvis.
a memorial service will be held on friday, june 12th, at 1:00 p. m., at grace bible fellowship, 1535 - 36th avenue, moline, il.
